<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport" />
    <title>MEETAGAIN</title>
    <meta content="" name="description" />
    <meta content="" name="keywords" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.3.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link href="assets/css/index.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') -%>
    <section class="landing-section" id="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="landing-content">
          <div class="landing-content-intro">
            <h1 class="subtitlepopin">
              Lost your online<strong> friend?</strong>
            </h1>
            <h2 class="">
              MeetAgain is a platform where you will able to search for your
              lost connections around the world!
            </h2>
            <div>
              <a href="#about" class="btn-get-started scrollto">Get Started</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img src="assets/images/friends.png" alt="" class="friends-img" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section" id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div
            class="col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12"
            data-scroll-reveal="enter left move 30px over 0.6s after 0.4s"
          >
            <img
              src="assets/images/left-image.png"
              class="rounded img-fluid d-block mx-auto"
              alt="App"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="right-text col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-sm-12 mobile-top-fix">
            <div class="left-heading">
              <h5 ">
                Aim to reunite people who drifted away due to unfortunate
                reasons
              </h5>
            </div>
            <div class="left-text">
              <p>
                Losing a online bestie!..Each one of you must have experienced
                it atleast once.Yeah,we too...That's what motivated us to create
                this platform. <br /><br />
                Create a account and submit your username and contact
                information.Hope your friends find you one day!
              </p>
              <a href="/signin" class="main-button">Create account</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <div class="hr"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section" id="about2">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="left-text col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-sm-12 mobile-bottom-fix">
            <div class="left-heading">
              <h5>A database for all the lost souls!</h5>
            </div>
            <p></p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <img src="assets/images/about-icon-01.png" alt="" />
                <div class="text">
                  <h6>Search by your friend's platform and username</h6>
                  <p>
                    Our database contains username and contact details submitted
                    by our users
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="assets/images/about-icon-02.png" alt="" />
                <div class="text">
                  <h6>Avail your friend's contact info</h6>
                  <p>Information such as Country, Discord , Email</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <img src="assets/images/about-icon-03.png" alt="" />
                <div class="text">
                  <h6>24/7 Support</h6>
                  <p>
                    If you have any question or comment, please
                    <a rel="nofollow" href="#">contact</a> us on MeetAgain.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div
            class="right-image col-lg-7 col-md-12 col-sm-12 mobile-bottom-fix-big"
            data-scroll-reveal="enter right move 30px over 0.6s after 0.4s"
          >
            <img
              src="assets/images/right-image.png"
              class="rounded img-fluid d-block mx-auto"
              alt="App"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="waitingfor-div">
      <span class="waitingfor-text"
        >What you waiting for? <br />
        Register now!</span
      >
    </div>
  <%- include('partials/footer') -%>
  </body>
</html>
